title: Autodesk Mudbox 2015 Mac OSX XFORCE
description:
Discover the new Features of Autodesk Mudbox 2015: Autodesk Mudbox 2015 release delivers powerful new toolsets a brief summary of the following new features and enhancements available in Autodesk Mudbox 2015.

Sending Maya image planes to Mudbox
Sending textures between Maya and Mudbox
Sending Maya blendshapes to Mudbox
Organizing paint layers as groups
Organizing sculpt layers as groups
Setting export paths for paint layers, groups, and channels
Picking the current Eyedropper paint layer color
Ability to paint stroke without the texture filter
Caliper tool enhancements
